    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款短小的自动化游戏，具有深刻的传说，但空间狭小！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造你的生产线！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271960/extras/6cbb852f34b70f79a47e91ffc4be805c.poster.avif?t=1741369773\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271960/extras/6cbb852f34b70f79a47e91ffc4be805c.webm?t=1741369773\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271960/extras/6cbb852f34b70f79a47e91ffc4be805c.mp4?t=1741369773\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁新区域和强大的机器！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271960/extras/29e5b06f1ef00b8002807470c7066acf.poster.avif?t=1741369773\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271960/extras/29e5b06f1ef00b8002807470c7066acf.webm?t=1741369773\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271960/extras/29e5b06f1ef00b8002807470c7066acf.mp4?t=1741369773\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用游戏中的 Wiki 获取一切信息！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271960/extras/59bfc9c6ac2b7b883039a5051f96c487.poster.avif?t=1741369773\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271960/extras/59bfc9c6ac2b7b883039a5051f96c487.webm?t=1741369773\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271960/extras/59bfc9c6ac2b7b883039a5051f96c487.mp4?t=1741369773\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用 InfiniBoxes™ 来欺骗空间！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271960/extras/2374cf4e317d2f2ad01e061f81bd417a.poster.avif?t=1741369773\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271960/extras/2374cf4e317d2f2ad01e061f81bd417a.webm?t=1741369773\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271960/extras/2374cf4e317d2f2ad01e061f81bd417a.mp4?t=1741369773\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271960/extras/3acbc50d6328725a63a8fcaf0469eb34.poster.avif?t=1741369773\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271960/extras/3acbc50d6328725a63a8fcaf0469eb34.webm?t=1741369773\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271960/extras/3acbc50d6328725a63a8fcaf0469eb34.mp4?t=1741369773\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271960/extras/82d23d0fc7de529ec17fce434afaf3c1.poster.avif?t=1741369773\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271960/extras/82d23d0fc7de529ec17fce434afaf3c1.webm?t=1741369773\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271960/extras/82d23d0fc7de529ec17fce434afaf3c1.mp4?t=1741369773\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能想出办法在有限的空间内建造一个高效的工厂吗？</p>",
